Frank BRATLEY and Anna Bratley, Appellants, v. UNITED STATES of America, Appellee. No. 6265. Circuit Court of Appeals, Ninth Circuit. Oct. 13, 1930.

Before RUDKIN and WILBUR, Circuit Judges, and NORCROSS,,District Judge.

PER CURIAM.

Pursuant to motion of appellee, ordered appeal dismissed for failure of appellants to file record and docket cause.
